name: QBZ-95 (GFL) - 2in1 ver.
description:
Updated Mar/5/2023:

New version trained with refined captions and new optimizer, saves 50% space and hopefully cured of overfitting. On top of that, details appeared to be more consistent on full weight too.

Features QBZ-95 (95式) from Girls' Frontline in her original costume & Summer Cicada bikini costume, trained on ACertainModel.

Release v1: Applying with a high weight (0.7-0.9) is recommended, going below will noticeably impact character robustness.

Release v2.0: Works well up to full weight (1.0), yet for some checkpoints lower weight (0.75-) will matter if you'd like to change entire outfits.

Prompts (v1)

  • Base: qbz95gfl, hairband, pantyhose, gloves, pleated skirt

  • Swimsuit: qbz95bkngfl, white bikini, thighhighs, sandals

Prompts (v2.0)

  • Base: jacket, black pantyhose, elbow gloves, pleated skirt

  • Swimsuit: white bikini, white thighhighs, sandals

    [Strengthening character cognition by prompting qbz95gfl/qbz95bkngfl is only advised for low weight applications]

Known Issue:

Hands seem to be a bit less stable than average due to her fingerless glove design.
